Subject: Westbrom External backup GCP - Build

Hi Adrian,

Hope you=92re doing fine.

As per our conversation last week, I=92ve listed down the high-level requir=
ements for External backup solution in GCP.

I=92ve looped in my team experts - @Narayan Iyer, Prashant<mailto:pnarayani=
yer@deloitte.co.uk> @Mohammad, Sadik<mailto:sadikmohammad@deloitte.co.uk> w=
ho has done a POC and successfully tested this backup workflow in GCP integ=
rated with Parity AWS.

The ask here is - to seek support in building this GCP backup transfer job =
workflow using automated deployment (terraform) and deploy the required con=
figurations in GCP.

Let me know if you require any further details in estimating this work item=
. Attaching the TDA approved design.

This is required for F&F go-live as part of NFR requirements.

Target Planned Date for Non-prod: 30-Apr
Production Deployment : TBD

I=92m happy to schedule call with your team member to detail the requiremen=
ts anytime.

GCP Services
Storage Transfer Service
Cloud Storage
Cloud KMS Key
Cloud Logging
Notification Topic
GCP
Create a Transfer Job in Scheduling mode with these parameters

  *   Source: Amazon S3
  *   AWS IAM Role ARN: arn:aws:iam::937245949235:role/dev-gcp-transfer-poc
  *   Destination: Google Cloud Storage
  *   Schedule: <<StartTime>>, Frequency
  *   Network Option: Google-managed private network
  *   Monitoring: Enable Cloud Logging
  *   Notification: Publish events on transfer status - Success, Failed, or=
 Aborted.
Security:

  *   Transfer job network traffic using Google-managed private network wit=
h AWS S3
  *   Encrypt destination cloud storage buckets with a dedicated Cloud KMS =
key
  *   Set retention policy and bucket to LOCKED mode to prevent deletion.
  *   Dedicated GCP project for Parity off-site backup storage


Kind regards,
Rahul Somasundaram
Associate Director | Deloitte MCS Limited
M: +447932473645


